.TH "DALMA\-GET_ACCOUNT" "" "August 2016" "NYUAD" "Dalma Manual"
.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
Here you will find information on how to get an account on \'Dalma\'
.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
This is a two\-step process:
.
.IP "1." 4
Request an account as instructed here \fIhttps://wikis\.nyu\.edu/display/ADRC/Getting+an+Account+on+Dalma\fR\. You need a valid NetID \fIhttp://www\.nyu\.edu/life/resources\-and\-services/information\-technology/getting\-started/netid\-and\-password\.html\fR to apply\.
.
.IP "2." 4
Ask your sponser \fIhttps://wikis\.nyu\.edu/display/NYUHPC/Account+Eligibility\fR to follow this link \fIhttps://wikis\.nyu\.edu/display/NYUHPC/How+to+approve+an+HPC+account+request\fR to approve your request\.
.
.IP "" 0
.
.P
The IIQ, NYU Identity Management service in NY will generate the account on Dalma in 2 business days\. You can then use your NetID and password to login\.
.
